          "description": "Made an online appointment last night and arrived next morning 45 minutes prior. They took me right in and the doctor/staff were excellent. Quick diagnosis and prescriptions were logged within 20 minutes. Would highly recommend if visiting from out of town and need something quickly.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aelUzWjVSeTE1UkhFemNqUjRTV2hyYUdKaWNtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xb647bfb0e680e6ad!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmZzU3Z5Ry15RHEzcjR4SWhraGJicmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
